对它几乎一无所知，”他<ins><a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/bethesda-the-elder-scrolls-6-details-years-away-192038484.html">当时发推文</a></ins>。 “因此，如果你现在而不是几年后向我询问细节，我就无法正确管理你的期望。”根据 Spencer 的评论， <em>《上古卷轴 VI》</em>可能会完全跳过当前一代的游戏机。上周，贝塞斯达游戏工作室创意总监托德·霍华德表示《<em>上古卷轴 6</em> 》“<ins> <a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.gamingbible.com/news/elder-scrolls-6-may-todd-howard-last-game-218259-20230613">可能是最后一场比赛</a></ins>他的职业生涯。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/the-elder-scrolls-vi-is-likely- Five-plus-years-away-says-xbox-chief-220526727.html?src=rss ]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/the-elder-scrolls-vi-is-likely-five-plus-years-away-says-xbox-chief-220526727.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> db4c849e-4266-44b2-a0b4-41b3141f53cc</guid><dc:creator>伊戈尔·博尼法西奇</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Sat, 24 Jun 2023 22:06:50 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1687644411</ingested><modified> 2023-06-24T22:06:54+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Igor Bonifacic]]></category><media:content height="1122" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-05/4111acb0-93c1-11ea-bbb7-9f335181b320" width="2000"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1122" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-05/4111acb0-93c1-11ea-bbb7-9f335181b320" width="2000"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media: