<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://twitter.com/netblocks/status/1672382720989593601?s=20">网络块</a></ins>（通过<ins><a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:The New York Times;elmt:;cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=c813ae39-7d58-41cb-ac66-ad830606ceef&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=The+New+York+Times&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAXN8GRGZwEdTXKMCf9lVhSi4pS730ALpSBPUA6c4J14T&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F06%2F23%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fgoogle-news-russia-prigozhin.html" class="rapid-with-clickid"><em>纽约时报</em></a></ins>），至少五家俄罗斯电信公司，包括 Rostelecom、U-LAN 和 Telplusl，正在阻止该国境内的网络用户访问新闻聚合器。谷歌没有立即回应 Engadget 的置评请求。 </p><div id="3e8689d025b9491ebf1c8f7697f3339b"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">⚠️ 已确认：指标显示， <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/Russia?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#Russia</a>的许多用户已无法使用 Google 新闻聚合平台；该事件发生之际，瓦格纳准军事组织与莫斯科之间的紧张关系加剧<a href="https://t.co/wXyzM0M79k">pic.twitter.com/wXyzM0M79k</a></p> - NetBlocks (@netblocks) <a href="https://twitter.com/netblocks/status/1672382720989593601?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2023 年 6 月 23 日</a></blockquote></div><p>周五晚间，瓦格纳集团雇佣兵从乌克兰越过边境，进入距离亚速海 20 英里的顿河畔罗斯托夫，并似乎占领了这座俄罗斯南部军事总部所在地的城市，而没有受到正规军的太大抵抗。军队。截至周六，<ins> <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:BBC;elmt:;cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=60e97fc3-5759-41aa-a73b-6317bb989588&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=BBC&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAVGw4V6iBMBgHxEsKVBBW_A3i-qRZNmqz_83w1YM5kpX&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Flive%2Fworld-europe-66006142%3Fns_mchannel%3Dsocial%26ns_source%3Dtwitter%26ns_campaign%3Dbbc_live%26ns_linkname%3D6496ae8c1babaa614a473145%2526Map%253A%2520The%2520key%2520locations%2520of%2520the%2520rebellion%25262023-06-24T09%253A02%253A43.658Z%26ns_fee%3D0%26pinned_post_locator%3Durn%3Aasset%3A9c85b8d4-f32c-4ea3-b846-84acd9329884%26pinned_p